commit a1532367a9d8bc7f1caa0a71217fd2ea164937ff
Author: Lucas Newman <lucas@future.fit>
Date:   Tue Mar 17 11:54:00 2026 -0700

    Add Chatterbox Turbo (#102)
    
    * add Chatterbox TTS model with voice cloning support
    
    Port of ResembleAI's Chatterbox TTS to MLX Swift. Includes both the
    Turbo (GPT-2 backbone) and Regular (LLaMA backbone) model variants
    with full S3Gen vocoder pipeline, T3 text-to-semantic generation,
    S3 tokenizer, CAMP+ speaker encoder, and HiFT-based neural vocoder.
    
    Features:
    - Text-to-speech with 24kHz output
    - Voice cloning via reference audio conditioning
    - Streaming generation support
    - Default conditioning from bundled speaker embeddings
    - Emotion tag support ([laugh], [sigh], etc.) via S3Gen pipeline
    
    Tested models:
    - mlx-community/chatterbox-turbo-fp16
    - mlx-community/Chatterbox-TTS-fp16
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
    
    * Co-authored-by: Eric Kryski <ekryski@bidali.com>
    
    Fix warnings and tests.
    
